author: CNN
description: Chuck Redd, the longtime host of the Kennedy Center’s annual Christmas Eve jazz performance said he canceled the concert following the board of trustees’ move to rename the facility for both the 35th president and President Donald Trump. CNN's Marshall Cohen reports.
title: Host cancels jazz show after Trump's name added to Kennedy Center

author: CNN
description:
After a harrowing and deadly Christmas Eve in California with rescues and evacuations amid widespread flooding and debris flow threats, another storm is battering the state Christmas Day, with more expected into Friday. 

Already, early on Christmas morning, a line of severe thunderstorms moved into Northern California with wind gusts in excess of 70 mph, setting off flash flooding in the San Francisco metro. 

00:00 California residents react to severe weather hitting their communities 
00:35 CNN meteorologist has the forecast as another storm impacts California 
03:15 A Southern California emergency responder discusses the situation in San Bernardino County 
06:01 A Los Angeles Fire Department captain details the danger facing Southern California  

#California #SevereWeather #News
title: Another storm slams California on Christmas Day

author: CNN
description: Pope Leo called for peace during his first Christmas celebration since becoming pontiff, encouraging the crowds in Vatican City to remember those suffering in Gaza whilst also calling for a ceasefire in Ukraine and other global conflicts. CNN Vatican Correspondent Christopher Lamb reports.
title: Pope Leo calls for peace in first Christmas as pontiff

author: CNN
description:
Tens of thousands of Ukrainian men are trying to avoid conscription as peace negotiations fail to yield substantial progress. Many of them are crossing into neighboring Romania through treacherous mountains, often in freezing temperatures. At least 19 have died trying.

Clarissa Ward hears from draft evaders, a man who claims to facilitate illegal crossings, and the head of the mountain rescue service that has saved hundreds of Ukrainians from the mountains since the beginning of Russia’s full-scale invasion.

#Ukraine #Russia #CNN
title: Why Ukraine’s draft evaders are dying in these icy mountains

description:
